                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wil",
                        "name": "wil",
                        "displayName": "Wil Sinclair",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "As Julien and I discussed over IRC, the better way to provide this functionality is to provide a route such as http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/downloads\/stable\/tar that interested parties can poll. We will consider such functionality in future website updates.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wil",
                        "name": "wil",
                        "displayName": "Wil Sinclair",
                        "active": true
